doFilter

public int doFilter(intradoc.data.Workspace ws,
                    intradoc.data.DataBinder db,
                    intradoc.common.ExecutionContext ec)
             throws intradoc.data.DataException,
                    intradoc.common.ServiceException
Hook into content server functionality during validateStandard, alterUserCredentials, and checkScheduledEvents hooks. During validateStandard, validateCoSign determines non-CoSign content and clears out CoSign values During alterUserCredentials, alterCoSign boosts user permissions allowing them to sign a document During checkScheduledEvents, CoSignFrequentEvent cleans up CS from stale (longer than 5min) signing sessions
